## `:deep(.p-*)` Whitelist (Exact 3-file Exception)

New `:deep(.p-*)` usage is forbidden except the following three files:

1. `packages/vue-ui/src/ProTable/ProTable.vue`
2. `apps/web-demo/src/views/login/index.vue`
3. `src/layouts/components/AnimateRouterView.vue`

Outside these files, targeting PrimeVue internal `.p-*` selectors is prohibited.

