## Anti-Patterns

```vue
<!-- FORBIDDEN -->
<InputText :pt="{ root: { class: 'bg-white text-black' } }" />
<Select :style="{ background: '#f8f9fa' }" />
<Button :pt="{ root: { class: 'bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700' } }" />
```
